data.chText: 反抗的神色 / 行动 / 表示
data.enText: a look/an act/a gesture of defiance

data.chText: 尽管国际上明令禁止，核试验又在进行了。
data.enText: Nuclear testing was resumed in defiance of an international ban.

value.def: Defiance is behaviour or an attitude which shows that you are not willing to obey someone.
If you do something in defiance of a person, rule, or law, you do it even though you know that you are not allowed to do it.

example.ex: Thousands of people have taken to the streets in defiance of the curfew.
example.tran: 成千上万的人不顾宵禁涌上街头。

value.tran: 违抗（某人）；无视，不顾(规定、法律等)

trans: 违抗（某人）；无视，不顾(规定、法律等)
